data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 2-story residence, built in 2019, offers a touch of modern comfort and style. With 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this home is perfect for you. Step inside to discover a spacious interior complete with tile floors and a well-equipped kitchen featuring granite countertops that seamlessly complement the contemporary design. Upstairs, you'll find a generously sized master bedroom, offering a peaceful retreat and an entertainment room perfect for games, movies, and sports. Conveniently located minutes from Hwy 6, Fort Bend Tollway, and the newly built Fort Bend Town Center, this home and neighborhood have everything to offer. Schedule your visit today to experience the charm of 2502 Crisp Apple. Listed for sale at 325,000, this Single-Family property boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2,133 square feet, and a 6,338 square feet lot size.
